hs_nirvanauk_lukedyson_2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/2024_thesmyths_nirvanauk_lukedyson_2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/2024_thesmyths_nirvanauk_lukedyson_2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/2024_thesmyths_nirvanauk_lukedyson_2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/2024_thesmyths_nirvanauk_lukedyson_2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/2024_thesmyths_nirvanauk_lukedyson_2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-smiths">史密斯</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/nirvana">Nirvana</a>致敬乐队昨晚（4 月 19 日）在 16 个月前的悲剧关闭后重新开放了布里克斯顿学院 - 粉丝们称赞它是“伦敦最好的场地”。</p><ul><li><b>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-smiths-tribute-band-brixton-academy-smyths-interview-re-open-3619686">史密斯致敬乐队重新开放布里克斯顿学院：“我们感激且谦虚”</a></b></li></ul><p>这座传奇的伦敦南部场馆自<a style="font-family: Verdana, BlinkMacSystemFont, -apple-system, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, 'Open Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/four-asake-fans-in-critical-condition-after-disturbance-at-brixton-academy-gig-3367923">2022 年 12 月以来一直关闭，此前发生了一场致命的人群拥挤事件</a>，导致两人死亡。这起悲惨事件发生在一场<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/asake">Asake</a>音乐会上，导致<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/tributes-paid-to-selfless-security-worker-killed-in-brixton-academy-asake-gig-crush-3370071">23 岁的 Gabrielle Hutchinson</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/woman-injured-during-asakes-o2-academy-brixton-show-dies-due-to-injuries-3368308">33 岁的 Rebecca Ikumelo</a>死亡。第三人情况危急。</p><p>自那时起，这座伦敦标志性场馆的未来就一直充满不确定性，直到 2023 年 12 月宣布<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/brixton-academy-allowed-to-retain-license-and-re-open-if-it-can-meet-robust-safety-rules-3498784">，如果能够满足“严格”的安全规则，将允许该场馆保留其许可证并重新开放</a>。请<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/these-are-the-77-robust-safety-conditions-brixton-academy-must-meet-for-re-opening-3502604">在此处查看已实施的 77 项措施的完整列表</a>。</p><p>昨晚，这些安全措施在场馆实施了新的安保和管理，球迷们被引导到场馆后面。其他措施包括新的票务系统和新的集中控制和指挥中心。 </p><figure style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/2024_brixtonacademy_lukedyson_2000x1270.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" /><figcaption class="wp-caption-text"> O2 布里克斯顿学院于 2024 年 4 月 19 日在伦敦重新开放 图片来源：Academy Music Group 的 Luke Dyson</figcaption></figure><p> Nirvana UK（向<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/nirvana">Nirvana</a>致敬）和 Smiths 致敬乐队 The Smyths 在一系列演出之前欢迎粉丝回到会场，接下来的演出将由<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/EDITORS">Editors</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-black-keys">The Black Keys</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/KAMASI-WASHINGTON">Kamasi Washington</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/arcade-fire">Arcade Fire</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/VAMPIRE-WEEKEND">Vampire Weekend</a>等乐队拉开序幕。几个月。</p><p>距 Nirvana 预定在该场地演出 30 年之际，Nirvana UK 翻唱了一系列经典歌曲，包括《Breed》、《In Bloom》、《Come As You Are》、《About A Girl》、《心形盒子”和“闻起来像青少年精神”。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/C59Hclyq86o/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100p