布莱恩·伊诺 (Brian Eno) 谈论在“强大”的新专辑《Get Real》中重新混音大卫·鲍伊 (David Bowie) 来应对气候变化https://www.nme.com/news/music/brian-eno-talks-remixing-david-bowie-on-powerful-new-release-get-real-to-combat-climate-change-3620200?utm_source= rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=brian-eno-talks-remixing-david-bowie-on-powerful-new-release-get-real-to-combat-climate-changeMax Pilley Fri, 19 Apr 2024 20:44:18 +0000 Music NewsNewsRockhttps://www.nme.com/?p=3620200 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/eno_bowie_1994.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/eno_bowie_1994.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/eno_bowie_1994-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/eno_bowie_1994-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/eno_bowie_1994-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/eno_bowie_1994-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/eno_bowie_1994-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “我认为这确实有效”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/brian-eno-talks-remixing-david-bowie-on-powerful-new-release-get-real-to-combat-climate-change-3620200">布莱恩·伊诺 (Brian Eno) 谈论在“强大”的新专辑“Get Real”中重新混音大卫·鲍伊 (David Bowie) 以应对气候变化的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/eno_bowie_1994.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/eno_bowie_1994.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/eno_bowie_1994-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/eno_bowie_1994-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/eno_bowie_1994-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/eno_bowie_1994-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/eno_bowie_1994-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/brian-eno">布莱恩·伊诺 (Brian Eno)</a>谈到了他<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/david-bowie">与大卫·鲍伊 (David Bowie)</a>合作的《Get Real》“强大的”，他现在正在重新制作这首歌曲，作为新的气候变化专辑项目的一部分。</p><p>这张<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/new-tracks-david-bowie-brian-eno-aurora-london-grammar-collaborating-with-nature-3619539">名为“Sounds Right”的唱片是由 Eno 与联合国博物馆在 4 月 22 日地球日之前共同制作的。Aurora</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/aurora">和</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/london-grammar">London Grammar</a>是被列入该计划的其他艺术家之一。项目。</p><p> “Sounds Right”还见证了Mother Nature 被认可为官方艺术家，她在主要流媒体平台上拥有自己的个人资料，发布的曲目包括来自自然世界的声音，包括海浪、风、暴雨和鸟鸣。作为认证艺术家，“Nature”还将在曲目播放时获得版税。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="变得真实 - 听起来正确的组合（壮举。自然）" width="696" height="522" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/6ekVur9r1Kc?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>鲍伊和伊诺的歌曲“Get Real”是对他们在“1.1”期间一起录制的一首歌曲的改编。上世纪 90 年代中期的“Outside”会议，新版本融入了鬣狗和野猪的录音，将其融入大自然。</p><p>在<a href="https://link.chtbl.com/midnightchats" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><i>午夜聊天</i></a>播客的新采访中，伊诺谈到了这首歌曲的创作以及选择加入动物声音。请听下面： </p><p><iframe title="Spotify 嵌入：第 127 集：布莱恩·伊诺" style="border-radius: 12px" width="100%" height="152" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen allow="autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; fullscreen; picture-in-picture" loading="lazy" src="https://open.spotify.com/embed/episode/7r0uCwdAfSijAtu2OyznQk?si=e234182c86b0422d&#038;utm_source=oembed"></iframe></p><p> “嗯，我这里有很多不同动物的录音，”他解释道。 “我希望歌曲中出现一些大型的、略带威胁性的动物。不是鸟和风之类的东西。所以我尝试了一只西伯利亚虎，那有点太压倒性了。我尝试了一些车。我一直很喜欢车，但在这种情况下它们听起来就像鸭子，这并不是完全相同的信息。我目前选定并正在合作的两只动物——我还没有完成这件作品——是鬣狗和野猪。”</p><p> “野猪听起来真不错。它们处于一种很难融入音乐的频率范围，但我正在努力。所以，是的，我们会有大卫、布里和一些野猪！”</p><p>伊诺接着说，他认为鲍伊会“喜欢它”，并补充道：“是的，他会说：‘对我来说听起来不错，布里。我认为我们应该继续这样做。”</p><p>伊诺解释说，他对与鲍伊一起录制原曲的记忆并不多，但补充道：“这是一首强有力的歌曲。非常好的歌词。通过这种新的容器，我们将其放入一首关于与地球关系的歌曲中，我认为它确实有效。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C55lfpUt6DP/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886 C532.1,33.886 524.886,41.1 524.886,50 C524.886,58.899 532.1,66.113 541,66.113 C